source: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_HELP<tab>Seems every other day we stop dealing in this or that type of tomestone. Inevitably, there comes a point when Rowena says that they're not worth the hassle anymore.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_HELP<tab>Des <var 33 ((Item)) 0DE8020302 /var>, vous dites<var 1D /var>? Rowena ne les prend plus, ça ne se vendait pas. Mais vous savez, dans ce métier, on trouve vite un autre filon<var 1D /var>!

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_TALK_NOT_HAVE<tab>Might be as I still have use for them, though. If you have any you don't need, bring them here and I'll give you something more desirable in exchange.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_TALK_NOT_HAVE<tab>Si vous vouliez, je pourrais vous les échanger contre des <var 33 ((Item)) 0DE8030302 /var>... Mais vous n'avez pas <var 33 ((Item)) 09E8020302 /var>, alors ça ne vous servira pas...

source: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_TALK_Q<tab>Might be as I still have use for them, though. If you have any you don't need, I'll give you something more desirable in exchange.
target: TEXT_CMNDEFTOMESTONEEXCHANGE_00153_TALK_Q<tab>Si vous voulez, je peux prendre vos <var 33 ((Item)) 0DE8020302 /var> et vous donner des <var 33 ((Item)) 0DE8040302 /var> en échange. Alors<var 1D /var>?
